rate,

00:16:02.928 --> 00:16:07.889
not only does the growth get
faster in an exponential way,

00:16:07.889 --> 00:16:12.341
but the rate of growth itself
grows so it's hyper-exponential

00:16:12.341 --> 00:16:13.009
growth.
 

00:16:13.009 --> 00:16:17.657
Now there's a--the whole issue
